CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Mid Penn Bancorp Inc operates in the financial services domain. It conducts commercial banking and trust business in the United States. Its range of services comprises mortgage and home equity loans, secured and unsecured consists and consumer loans, lines of credit, construction financing, farm loans, community development, and local government loans, and various types of time and demand deposits.
